~: switch the caps of cursor word
3~: switch the caps of 3 words from the beginning of the cursor
g~~: switch the caps of current line
gUU: switch the caps of current line to uppercase
guu: switch the caps of current line to lowercase
gUaw(gUiw): switch the words of cursor to uppercase
guaw(guiw): switch the words of cursor to lowercase 


